& [SLMSlice27ProviderInternalFacultyReport] is the source-complete slice for provider internal faculty evidence
  + [slice_id] is SLM-27
  + [status] is source_complete_policy_gated
  + [effort] is M
  + [risk] is medium
  + [depends_on] is SLM-04, SLM-05, SLM-08, SLM-22, SLM-26
  + [contract] is slm_project/specifications/contracts/SLM_Provider_Internal_Faculty_Report_Contract.sop
  + [deliverable] is provider-side faculty report structs and deliberation references
  + [completion_review] is slm_project/planning/project_manager/reviews/SLM_Manager_Batch_Review_2026-06-21.sop

  & [WorkCompleted] is the slice result
    + [added] is HemispherePerspective
    + [added] is ProviderFacultyVote
    + [added] is ProviderFacultyVeto
    + [added] is ProviderFacultyReport
    + [added] is ProviderSuggestion::faculty_report constructor
    + [updated] is ProviderDeliberation faculty_report_refs

  & [RemainingGate] is executable verification
    + [blocked_by] is Windows Application Control policy for Cargo-generated executables
    + [allowed_validation] is source scan and SOP review only
